<L>__{interior train station day}
<A>__{the train pulls into the station. there are hundreds of people awaiting the arrival of the dalai lama hundreds of "china pictorial", red cheeked, chinese communists; men, women and children, waving little red flags. tenzin gyatso steps off the train and there is a roar of approval. song breaks out the people's republic national anthem. the young man is overwhelmed. we begin to sense that something is wrong, something is artificial. the people's presence is demanded here today. this is a forced display of regard.}
